weren't allowed to drink it.

00:10:24.125 --> 00:10:27.228 position:19% line:83% align:start
Because then you might
turn into a baby and disappear.

00:10:27.361 --> 00:10:28.530 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:10:28.929 --> 00:10:30.498 position:19% line:89% align:start
With all that in mind,

00:10:30.831 --> 00:10:32.833 position:10% line:89% align:start
a lot more things make sense.

00:10:33.067 --> 00:10:35.537 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're like your mother.
Don't you think?

00:10:35.669 --> 00:10:36.704 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:10:37.138 --> 00:10:38.839 position:10% line:89% align:start
You really think that's true?

00:10:38.973 --> 00:10:42.243 position:19% line:83% align:start
I mean, just going off
of everything you've told me.

00:10:42.443 --> 00:10:45.346 position:7% line:83% align:start
Like the fact that both of you
love drinking alcohol.

00:10:45.547 --> 00:10:48.349 position:16% line:83% align:start
Or what about how you're
both cute when you're drunk?

00:10:48.617 --> 00:10:50.117 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, that doesn't mean a thing.

00:10:50.251 --> 00:10:51.852 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everyone around here
gets like that

00:10:51.986 --> 00:10:53.387 position:16% line:89% align:start
with a couple of drinks.

00:10:53.522 --> 00:10:54.556 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:54.688 --> 00:10:55.689 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[knocking]
-Huh?

00:10:55.823 --> 00:10:56.857 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

00:10:56.991 --> 00:10:58.527 position:24% line:89% align:start
[door creaks open]

00:10:58.659 --> 00:11:00.629 position:38% line:83% align:start
Any luck
finding more about yourself?

00:11:00.761 --> 00:11:02.029 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, plenty.

00:11:02.229 --> 00:11:04.732 position:21% line:83% align:start
We're already getting
into the afternoon hours.

00:11:04.865 --> 00:11:07.401 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why don't the two of you
join us for lunch?

00:11:08.269 --> 00:11:09.403 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bird chirping]

00:11:10.271 --> 00:11:12.907 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Oh, that was wonderful.

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:14.475 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thank you for the meal.

00:11:14.609 --> 00:11:17.178 position:21% line:83% align:start
I think a little beer
would be perfect right now.

00:11:17.311 --> 00:11:18.379 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you say?

00:11:18.812 --> 00:11:20.181 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're getting me worried.

00:11:20.347 --> 00:11:22.383 position:19% line:83% align:start
You know when to stop,
don't you?

00:11:22.517 --> 00:11:23.552 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:11:23.918 --> 00:11:25.654 position:38% line:83% align:start
