00:11:25.819 --> 00:11:27.656 position:33% line:83% align:start
I've got just
what you're fixing for.

00:11:27.788 --> 00:11:31.125 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'd know the voice that makes
the mountains shake anywhere.

00:11:31.358 --> 00:11:33.127 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hi, Natalia!

00:11:34.028 --> 00:11:35.296 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's been way too long.

