-[chuckling]

00:11:44.573 --> 00:11:45.674 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's right.

00:11:45.806 --> 00:11:47.408 position:21% line:89% align:start
This lady is Natalia.

00:11:47.542 --> 00:11:50.411 position:10% line:83% align:start
She's been an important part
of the staff since I was a kid.

00:11:50.579 --> 00:11:53.047 position:19% line:83% align:start
You must be the girlie
who came here from Japan.

00:11:53.214 --> 00:11:55.316 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah. I'm Teru Momijiyama.

00:11:55.482 --> 00:11:57.718 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, we may not
have much around here,

00:11:57.851 --> 00:11:59.453 position:16% line:89% align:start
but enjoy what there is.

00:11:59.588 --> 00:12:01.388 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's so generous of you.

00:12:02.856 --> 00:12:04.892 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's time to catch up, Pesha.

00:12:05.092 --> 00:12:07.328 position:10% line:89% align:start
We're long overdue, Natalia.

00:12:07.728 --> 00:12:09.964 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:12:11.633 --> 00:12:13.167 position:44% line:83% align:start
