It looks easy.

00:12:15.135 --> 00:12:17.471 position:7% line:83% align:start
[NATALIA] Tell me, what brought
the two of you out here?

00:12:17.606 --> 00:12:20.241 position:30% line:83% align:start
I don't suppose
memory lane came a-callin'?

00:12:20.374 --> 00:12:21.308 position:38% line:89% align:start
I guess.

00:12:21.842 --> 00:12:24.912 position:13% line:83% align:start
While I scanned the albums,
I remembered more of my days

00:12:25.045 --> 00:12:26.480 position:21% line:89% align:start
here than I expected.

00:12:27.047 --> 00:12:29.216 position:30% line:83% align:start
I was nostalgic
the entire time.

00:12:29.483 --> 00:12:32.052 position:19% line:83% align:start
[NATALIA] If I recall,
you were a nightmare

00:12:32.186 --> 00:12:33.387 position:21% line:83% align:start
