our family.

00:12:33.521 --> 00:12:35.289 position:13% line:83% align:start
I couldn't get a damn word
out of you.

00:12:35.422 --> 00:12:37.358 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Was I really that bad?

00:12:38.259 --> 00:12:41.829 position:10% line:83% align:start
Nowadays, you're starting to
look more and more like Lenya.

00:12:42.096 --> 00:12:43.531 position:19% line:89% align:start
