supposedly changed.

00:13:34.815 --> 00:13:35.983 position:21% line:89% align:start
But nothing's changed

00:13:36.116 --> 00:13:37.284 position:21% line:83% align:start
in the little corners
of the world

00:13:37.418 --> 00:13:39.253 position:35% line:83% align:start
