off, dear.

00:13:43.957 --> 00:13:45.826 position:10% line:89% align:start
No, it's fascinating, really.

00:13:46.193 --> 00:13:47.529 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now that I think of it.

00:13:47.662 --> 00:13:49.830 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're looking to explore
some old memories, right?

00:13:49.963 --> 00:13:52.933 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why don't you take a gander
at some of my old photo albums?

00:13:53.067 --> 00:13:54.234 position:35% line:89% align:start
Great idea.

00:13:54.368 --> 00:13:56.136 position:27% line:83% align:start
You wouldn't have
seen much of her before,

00:13:56.270 --> 00:13:58.105 position:7% line:89% align:start
but I'll bet Lenya is in those!

00:13:58.238 --> 00:13:59.206 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm?!

00:13:59.340 --> 00:14:00.974 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Now I've just got to see that!

00:14:01.108 --> 00:14:02.777 position:7% line:89% align:start
I wonder what she looked like.

00:14:02.910 --> 00:14:04.912 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hurry up and get those albums!

00:14:05.079 --> 00:14:07.114 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ISAAK]
Oh, if you insist.

00:14:09.584 --> 00:14:10.652 position:33% line:89% align:start
Here you go.

00:14:10.951 --> 00:14:13.420 position:44% line:83% align:start
Hmm.
Oh, this takes me way back!

00:14:13.555 --> 00:14:16.758 position:30% line:83% align:start
Oh, look at us
like two peas in a pod!

00:14:16.890 --> 00:14:18.593 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NATALIA]
Aren't we the cutest?

00:14:18.727 --> 00:14:20.595 position:7% line:89% align:start
Where are you in here, Natalia?

00:14:21.462 --> 00:14:22.496 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's me.

00:14:24.498 --> 00:14:25.533 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

