like a princess back then.

00:14:55.429 --> 00:14:58.031 position:21% line:83% align:start
The girl next to her
as gorgeous as well.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:14:59.634 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:00.067 --> 00:15:01.402 position:30% line:89% align:start
