you wouldn't happen to be...

00:15:14.081 --> 00:15:15.149 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:15.416 --> 00:15:16.851 position:47% line:83% align:start
Oh,
you hit the nail on the head.

00:15:16.984 --> 00:15:18.853 position:13% line:89% align:start
That pretty lady is Lenya.

00:15:19.687 --> 00:15:20.988 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE ORPHAN 8A]
Sorry, could you get that?

00:15:21.121 --> 00:15:22.322 position:24% line:83% align:start
