to be a long-lost sister.

00:16:05.800 --> 00:16:08.335 position:21% line:89% align:start
But in this picture,

00:16:09.336 --> 00:16:10.772 position:21% line:89% align:start
they're too similar.

00:16:10.905 --> 00:16:12.473 position:21% line:89% align:start
Like it's really her.

00:16:14.241 --> 00:16:16.343 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
But there's no way that's true.

00:16:16.977 --> 00:16:18.479 position:33% line:89% align:start
Since my mama

00:16:19.246 --> 00:16:20.648 position:30% line:89% align:start
isn't with us.

00:16:22.449 --> 00:16:23.450 position:38% line:89% align:start
[howling]

00:16:24.051 --> 00:16:25.553 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[screaming]
-[gasps]

00:16:26.588 --> 00:16:27.689 position:30% line:89% align:start
What was that?

00:16:28.523 --> 00:16:29.624 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't tell me...

00:16:30.859 --> 00:16:31.893 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh?

00:16:32.426 --> 00:16:34.361 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[door opens]
-Huh?

00:16:34.495 --> 00:16:38.465 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:16:38.867 --> 00:16:39.901 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh?

00:16:40.033 --> 00:16:41.769 position:7% line:89% align:start
What in the world is going on?

00:16:42.135 --> 00:16:43.270 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[crying]
-[gasps]

00:16:43.403 --> 00:16:44.973 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[crying]
-Kids, come here, quick.

00:16:45.138 --> 00:16:47.474 position:10% line:89% align:start
Tell me what's happening. Oh.

00:16:47.609 --> 00:16:49.142 position:27% line:89% align:start
We-We don't know.

00:16:49.911 --> 00:16:52.614 position:24% line:83% align:start
There was a strange
girl we didn't recognize

00:16:52.747 --> 00:16:53.815 position:16% line:89% align:start
and she walked up to us.

00:16:53.948 --> 00:16:55.750 position:21% line:89% align:start
And froze her solid!

00:16:56.818 --> 00:16:58.352 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's going on?

00:16:58.686 --> 00:16:59.854 position:24% line:89% align:start
We've got to help.

00:17:00.053 --> 00:17:01.623 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let's Heart-Shift.

00:17:02.857 --> 00:17:05.392 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[SPIRIT] Just do it.
-I guess we have to!

00:17:05.560 --> 00:17:06.594 position:38% line:89% align:start
[tapping]

00:17:07.562 --> 00:17:09.296 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:17:19.674 --> 00:17:21.208 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Teru,

00:17:21.341 --> 00:17:22.710 position:13% line:89% align:start
make sure that kid is safe.

00:17:22.844 --> 00:17:24.077 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh, sure!

00:17:25.013 --> 00:17:26.246 position:41% line:89% align:start
Pesha.

00:17:26.848 --> 00:17:27.882 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
All this ice.

00:17:28.081 --> 00:17:29.383 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is Tzveta here?

00:17:29.784 --> 00:17:32.419 position:27% line:83% align:start
But her timing is
more than peculiar.

00:17:33.387 --> 00:17:35.322 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is she after me?

00:17:36.290 --> 00:17:37.525 position:35% line:89% align:start
[straining]

00:17:39.326 --> 00:17:41.395 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, are you all right?

00:17:43.731 --> 00:17:44.999 position:35% line:83% align:start
-S-So, so..
-You must be cold.

00:17:45.132 --> 00:17:46.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
But everything's gonna be
okay now.

00:17:46.968 --> 00:17:48.002 position:41% line:83% align:start
-S-S...
-Huh?

00:17:48.268 --> 00:17:50.370 position:10% line:89% align:start
Her clothing looks familiar.

00:17:50.805 --> 00:17:52.607 position:38% line:89% align:start
So, so...

00:17:52.974 --> 00:17:55.075 position:38% line:89% align:start
Surprise!

00:17:55.777 --> 00:17:56.811 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:58.546 --> 00:18:00.515 position:27% line:83% align:start
'Kay, so, how was
my opening act?

00:18:00.648 --> 00:18:04.084 position:24% line:83% align:start
Wasn't it hilarious
how I was frozen solid?

00:18:04.217 --> 00:18:05.452 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kufufu!

00:18:06.219 --> 00:18:07.989 position:19% line:89% align:start
You can call me Kufufu!

00:18:08.121 --> 00:18:10.658 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was born to make sure
the whole world's got a

00:18:10.792 --> 00:18:12.994 position:30% line:83% align:start
smile plastered
across their face!

00:18:13.493 --> 00:18:16.363 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna take "kill
'em with comedy" too far!

00:18:16.496 --> 00:18:17.532 position:47% line:89% align:start
JK!

00:18:18.398 --> 00:18:20.001 position:21% line:89% align:start
So, does that mean...

00:18:20.133 --> 00:18:21.869 position:13% line:89% align:start
you belong to Amarariruku?

00:18:22.003 --> 00:18:23.303 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:18:23.437 --> 00:18:25.540 position:21% line:83% align:start
You wanna hear about
my dramatic backstory?

00:18:25.840 --> 00:18:27.075 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kufufu...

00:18:27.274 --> 00:18:29.978 position:21% line:83% align:start
Okay. I'll confirm I
belong to Amarariruku.

00:18:30.110 --> 00:18:33.081 position:7% line:83% align:start
And you're not the only member
of your crew here right now!

00:18:33.213 --> 00:18:35.115 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tzveta's around here too,
isn't she?

00:18:35.248 --> 00:18:37.652 position:30% line:83% align:start
Is Tzveta here?
Of course!

00:18:37.785 --> 00:18:42.122 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Silly, why else do you think
we'd come here? -[sighs]

00:18:42.657 --> 00:18:45.560 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you don't shut up,
you'll tell them everything.

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:46.794 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:47.160 --> 00:18:48.863 position:19% line:89% align:start
Good to see you, Pesha.

00:18:49.496 --> 00:18:51.766 position:33% line:83% align:start
I assume that
you're feeling better.

00:18:53.001 --> 00:18:55.603 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] Sorry about that,
I went too far.

00:18:55.737 --> 00:18:58.740 position:13% line:83% align:start
But in my defense, you did
something really mean to me,

00:18:58.873 --> 00:19:00.508 position:19% line:89% align:start
like some awful adult.

00:19:00.742 --> 00:19:02.110 position:30% line:89% align:start
I want answers.

00:19:02.309 --> 00:19:04.344 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why are you here
of all places?

00:19:04.846 --> 00:19:07.115 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
She looks a lot like mama.

00:19:07.447 --> 00:19:09.249 position:21% line:89% align:start
But it can't be her.

00:19:10.518 --> 00:19:13.387 position:30% line:83% align:start
Stigma uses the
darkness in people's hearts.

00:19:14.287 --> 00:19:17.825 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm sure he's just trying to
take advantage of my weakness.

00:19:20.528 --> 00:19:23.163 position:24% line:83% align:start
This has got to be
some kind of trick.

00:19:23.965 --> 00:19:25.733 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why am I here, you say?

00:19:25.867 --> 00:19:28.803 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, it's funny.

00:19:29.037 --> 00:19:30.270 position:10% line:89% align:start
I don't have a single memory

00:19:30.404 --> 00:19:32.540 position:27% line:83% align:start
before I woke up
at the North Pole.

00:19:32.674 --> 00:19:33.407 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:19:33.541 --> 00:19:35.710 position:16% line:89% align:start
So, I wonder why myself.

00:19:36.443 --> 00:19:37.979 position:10% line:89% align:start
There's something about you.

00:19:38.112 --> 00:19:41.916 position:13% line:83% align:start
Something about this place
that stirs my memories a bit.

00:19:43.084 --> 00:19:44.519 position:7% line:89% align:start
Perhaps you were the one person

00:19:44.652 --> 00:19:46.888 position:33% line:83% align:start
I cared about
more than anything.

00:19:47.287 --> 00:19:50.758 position:35% line:83% align:start
Or perhaps
the person I hated the most.

00:19:51.025 --> 00:19:52.225 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's enough of that.

00:19:52.359 --> 00:19:53.761 position:16% line:89% align:start
Just who are you anyway?

00:19:54.095 --> 00:19:56.731 position:10% line:83% align:start
And why are you the spitting
image of my mama?

00:19:57.065 --> 00:19:58.766 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh. Huh?

00:19:59.199 --> 00:20:00.902 position:10% line:89% align:start
I wonder if that's the reason

00:20:01.035 --> 00:20:04.271 position:24% line:83% align:start
why Pesha rolls off
the tongue so easily.

00:20:05.472 --> 00:20:07.075 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
[shouts]

00:20:07.207 --> 00:20:08.176 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:20:08.308 --> 00:20:09.443 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:20:09.844 --> 00:20:12.379 position:13% line:83% align:start
Cut the crap with the lies
and cheap imitations.

00:20:12.680 --> 00:20:14.682 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're going to piss me off!

00:20:14.882 --> 00:20:16.249 position:33% line:89% align:start
How bizarre!

00:20:16.517 --> 00:20:18.853 position:27% line:83% align:start
For some reason,
when I'm looking at you,

00:20:19.187 --> 00:20:21.254 position:13% line:89% align:start
my heart feels alive again.

00:20:21.723 --> 00:20:22.990 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
To be frank,

00:20:23.124 --> 00:20:25.459 position:35% line:83% align:start
my emotions
are as hazy as my memories.

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:29.262 position:21% line:83% align:start
But Stigma's ideology
has earned my approval.

00:20:29.964 --> 00:20:31.264 position:35% line:89% align:start
This world,

00:20:31.398 --> 00:20:33.901 position:24% line:83% align:start
it cost me nothing
but pain and suffering.

00:20:34.035 --> 00:20:35.837 position:27% line:89% align:start
My cold reality.

00:20:35.970 --> 00:20:39.006 position:19% line:83% align:start
I believe I hated it to
the core of my being.

00:20:40.340 --> 00:20:42.043 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
But not this place.

00:20:42.176 --> 00:20:44.344 position:10% line:89% align:start
I felt warm when I was here.

00:20:44.712 --> 00:20:47.515 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wish I could spend
eternity in these walls.

00:20:47.782 --> 00:20:50.484 position:30% line:83% align:start
As I enter this
nostalgic landscape.

00:20:50.618 --> 00:20:54.387 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can feel the gentle
winds of home embrace me.

00:20:56.023 --> 00:20:58.593 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's better than I could ever
imagine it feeling.

00:20:58.726 --> 00:21:00.561 position:16% line:89% align:start
I knew my place was here.

00:21:00.695 --> 00:21:02.496 position:7% line:89% align:start
What do you mean "your place?"

00:21:03.296 --> 00:21:04.799 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's like he said,

00:21:05.233 --> 00:21:06.534 position:10% line:89% align:start
within every person's heart,

00:21:06.667 --> 00:21:08.603 position:30% line:83% align:start
there's a place
made for you alone.

00:21:08.836 --> 00:21:11.873 position:13% line:83% align:start
A place to separate reality
from your dreams.

00:21:12.272 --> 00:21:13.808 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kufufu!

00:21:14.208 --> 00:21:15.576 position:13% line:89% align:start
Somewhere the never ending

00:21:15.710 --> 00:21:18.179 position:21% line:83% align:start
torment of existence
cannot reach you.

00:21:18.679 --> 00:21:20.148 position:44% line:83% align:start
-No.
-[cracking]

00:21:20.280 --> 00:21:22.550 position:24% line:83% align:start
There's only peace
everlasting here.

00:21:22.717 --> 00:21:24.351 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[crashing]
-[gasps]

00:21:24.852 --> 00:21:28.288 position:16% line:83% align:start
And you already know the
name he bestowed on this place.

00:21:28.556 --> 00:21:30.658 position:7% line:89% align:start
A name you've all heard before.

00:21:34.461 --> 00:21:35.730 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is that?!

00:21:37.698 --> 00:21:39.934 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:21:40.067 --> 00:21:41.468 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:21:43.137 --> 00:21:44.172 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exploding]

00:21:44.404 --> 00:21:46.641 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
Amarariruku.

00:21:47.241 --> 00:21:51.078 position:16% line:83% align:start
I accept the cold reality
no more.

00:21:52.180 --> 00:21:53.380 position:33% line:89% align:start
From now on,

00:21:53.514 --> 00:21:55.550 position:16% line:89% align:start
we'll live our life here.

00:21:56.818 --> 00:21:59.787 position:27% line:83% align:start
Enveloped in the
warm days of youth.

00:22:00.288 --> 00:22:01.488 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:22:01.956 --> 00:22:02.957 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:03.090 --> 00:22:04.792 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let me welcome you

00:22:04.926 --> 00:22:07.562 position:33% line:83% align:start
to the inner
depths of my heart.

00:22:08.495 --> 00:22:10.765 position:30% line:89% align:start
My Amarariruku.

